ange box can be helpful to use during Black Friday. <\/em><\/p>\n<p><strong>\u26a1 Get started with Smart Bidding in a flash <\/strong>using our free, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/resources\/smart-bidding?cid=Web_WS_InContent_Guide_SmartBidding_Download&amp;itm_source=wordstream&amp;itm_medium=blog&amp;itm_campaign=incontent_links\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">fool-proof guide to Smart Bidding<\/a>!<\/p>\n<h3>Use Meta Advantage+ to reach holiday shoppers<\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/meta-advantage-plus\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Advantage+ within Meta Ads<\/a> is a suite of automated solutions meant to help streamline your campaign buildout and management. For Black Friday, you could use Advantage+ audiences or placements to help build out your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/facebook-ad-targeting\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">campaign targeting<\/a> to reach users outside of your usual lists.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/meta-advantage-plus-audience-and-placements-e1760985268155.webp\" alt=\"meta ads advantage+ - advantage plus audience and placements in facebook ads\" width=\"813\" height=\"547\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-84704 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/meta-advantage-plus-audience-and-placements-e1760985268155.webp 813w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/meta-advantage-plus-audience-and-placements-e1760985268155-480x270.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 813px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<h3>Import campaigns into Microsoft Ads to maximize your reach<\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/microsoft-ads\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Microsoft Ads<\/a> should be a no-brainer when running Black Friday advertising campaigns, as it\u2019s easy to get up and running on there in a flash. You could import your Black Friday campaigns from other ad platforms, like Google Ads or Meta Ads, to quickly place your seasonal ads across the Microsoft Ads network, which includes <a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/advertise-on-bing\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">high-value placements like the Bing Search Results Page<\/a>, and more.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/microsoft-ads-auto-import.webp\" alt=\"microsoft ads - autoimport\" width=\"422\" height=\"600\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-94776 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/microsoft-ads-auto-import.webp 422w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/microsoft-ads-auto-import-211x300.webp 211w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 422px) 100vw, 422px\" \/><\/p>\n<div id=\"free-black-friday-marketing-template\" div=\"\">\n<h2>Black Friday marketing planning template<\/h2>\n<p>Make a copy of this <a href=\"https:\/\/docs.google.com\/spreadsheets\/d\/1c1S8atQHCMi_of8d0A9My-2HSVLD2xnPExuWjv-IojA\/copy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">free planning template<\/a> to jumpstart your Black Friday marketing!<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/black-friday-marketing-template.webp\" alt=\"black friday marketing template - template preview screenshot\" width=\"912\" height=\"633\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-95039 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/black-friday-marketing-template.webp 912w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/black-friday-marketing-template-480x333.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 912px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/docs.google.com\/spreadsheets\/d\/1c1S8atQHCMi_of8d0A9My-2HSVLD2xnPExuWjv-IojA\/copy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopene